item.description:
Basic shortcodes The following content:
{{&lt; tabgroup &gt;}}
{{&lt; tab name=&quot;Hello&quot; &gt;}}
Hello World!
{{&lt; /tab &gt;}}
{{&lt; tab name=&quot;Goodbye&quot; &gt;}}
Goodbye Everybody!
{{&lt; /tab &gt;}}
{{&lt; /tabgroup &gt;}}
Will generate:
Hello Hello World! Goodbye Goodbye Everybody! Right alighment You can also align the tabs to the right:
{{&lt; tabgroup align=&quot;right&quot; &gt;}}
{{&lt; tab name=&quot;Hello&quot; &gt;}}
Hello World!
{{&lt; /tab &gt;}}
{{&lt; tab name=&quot;Goodbye&quot; &gt;}}
Goodbye Everybody!
{{&lt; /tab &gt;}}
{{&lt; /tabgroup &gt;}}
Giving you this look:
